    "This left us with a final set of 20 cases, eight of which are class action cases.",
    "More details of our case selection process, including reasons for excluding specific cases, can be found in \"Appendix 2.1\".",
    "To craft our prompt for this aspect of our study, we used ChatGPT's online user interface.",
